==伴星==
目前已知三顆B型次矮星擁有行星。[[飛馬座V391|飛馬座V391]]是第一個知道有行星存在的B型次矮星，[[室女座HW|室女座HW]]已知有兩顆行星<ref name="Heber"/>；[[克卜勒70|克卜勒70]]已知有兩顆行星，並可能有第三顆存在<ref name=nature480_496>{{citation | display-authors=1 | first1=S. | last1=Charpinet | first2=G. | last2=Fontaine | first3=P. | last3=Brassard | first4=E. M. | last4=Green | first5=V. | last5=Van Grootel | first6=S. K. | last6=Randall | first7=R. | last7=Silvotti | first8=A. S. | last8=Baran | first9=R. H. | last9=Østensen | date=December 21, 2011 | title=A compact system of small planets around a former red-giant star | journal=Nature | volume=480 | pages=496–499 | doi=10.1038/nature10631 }}</ref>。

